reviewText: the second part is good. bought the whole thing in one go

This is just as good as the Blu-Ray version, as it's got the same English Dub by Animax as well as the Blu-Ray version, and it's at a cheaper price.

So if you want to see Animax's English Dub of CardCaptor Sakura, but can't afford the Blu-Ray edition, then NIS America's 3 DVD Set's are the ones for you. :)
Even though it was damaged helpful with filing a claim with the custom charge as they are the reason it broke very happy with how they are dealing with it happy with the dvd
